message.body: Could you please bring books for me to borrow to PCA tomorrow so I can pick them up? What time is your shift? :)
U got it. 3-7p if u can't make it there I can leave in bag by punk desk
Perfect! I should make it but good idea just in case. It will b nice to see you for a minute! I'm trying to study for finals. Ugh.
Finals? Yikes !! If u are in study groove don't fret over running over. I'll just see ya some other thurs or sat. No stress!
It's ok! I would love to run by!
